HEADWORD: Opisthography
<hw>Op`is*thog"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>'o`pisqen</grk> behind + <ets>-graphy</ets>.]</ety> <def>A writing
